Cook whipping cream in a small saucepan over medium heat, stirring occasionally, until almost boiling. Set aside. Sprinkle SPLENDA(R) Sugar Blend for Baking in a heavy saucepan; sprinkle with water. Cook over low heat, stirring constantly. until SPLENDA(R) Sugar Blend for Baking melts and turns light golden. Gradually add hot whipping cream.(Mixture will lump). Cook over low heat, stirring constantly, until mixture is smooth and comes to a boil. Boil 5 minutes, stirring constantly. Stir in butter.